{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Caspian_Plague",
  "title": "The Caspian Plague",
  "summary": "At a medical center ravaged by the Caspian plague, the dying researcher Kadgie and the scarred, blood-coughing Morganna struggle to survive while Kadgie takes a desperate holovid call from her superior and lover, Adlerson, on Sullust. Adlerson can offer only the promise that Dagny is harvesting the curative moss and that help will come 'soon,' which enrages the failing Morganna, who accuses him of letting them die rather than defying his Imperial masters. As Kadgie repeatedly collapses, coughing up blood, the conversation becomes an anguished tug-of-war between Adlerson's pleas to hold on and Morganna's furious demands for the cure now. Dr. Angalun Faust storms in with his staff, ordering treatments and forcing both women toward bacta against Kadgie's stubborn insistence on saving the medicine for others. The transmission finally cuts as Morganna passes out and Faust takes charge, refusing to let either woman die.",
